    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nEven with load set to false, pack.add() still registers all plugins in spec, causing them to be sourced during startup.\n\nThis can be partially worked around by saving and restoring the RTP from before running pack.add(), but you still lose startup time to the initial registration step.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nCould an option be added to pack.add() to skip the registration step?",
